SweetTooltip is a collection of simply awesome tooltip crafted using jQuery & CSS3, yes it's imageless.

Usage : 
Include jQuery.js, sweet-tooltip.js and sweet-tooltip.css, then call tooltip by following code :
<a href="#" 
	class="sweet-tooltip" 
	data-style-tooltip="tooltip-style-name" 
	data-text-tooltip="Tooltip text">
Your link
</a>

There are seven tooltip style available :
1. Sweet Strong, tooltip style name : tooltip-sweet-strong
2. Mini Slick, tooltip style name : tooltip-mini-slick
3. Big Grey, tooltip style name : tooltip-big-grey
4. Nightly, tooltip style name : tooltip-nightly
5. Shiny Red,  tooltip style name : tooltip-shiny-red
6. Soft Blue,  tooltip style name : tooltip-soft-blue
7. Big Yellow,  tooltip style name : tooltip-big-yellow